<br>
For earrings, currently I am looking at Vrryin's (sp?) Earring of Insanity from Vulak and Earring of the Icecaster from Jorleag, although I am not sure this is the best route.  It might be better to skip the Vulak earring since it has no mana and do the Sanctum Guardian Earring instead.<br>
<br>
For rings, I have a ring of superiority that I love and am trying to decide between the 10th Dain Ring and the new Chardok ring.  Currently I swap between Ring of Winter and Tunarean Signet Ring on that finger.<br>
<br>
What do you think is the ultimate ring/earring combo?<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukalinn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kalinn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(11/29/01 10:55:14 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://members.home.net/azurecrayon/wolf.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Best Jewelry Combination</span><hr size=1> if you are hunting in ntov and have a chance to get loot from vulak and jorleag, then you arent likely to get a sanctum guardians earring as that requires ally cov faction which you screw to hunt in ntov.  if faction wasnt an issue, i'd say go for sanctum earring and the one from vulak.<br>
<br>
faction is an issue on the rings as well, since you wear a ring off dain himself.  dain faction is very hard to raise if you are kos from killing him, and you must have high dain faction for 10th ring.  but the 10th dain ring is definately better than the second chardok ring (wait and see if that series has another ring as the third item isnt a ring).  even the 9th dain ring is very nice, and since its a clickable, great for high end raiding which you need to get the earrings =) <p>-K<br>
